      <prov id="DLM1122579" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">33</label>
        <heading>Copying by librarians for collections of other libraries</heading>
        <prov.body>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="no"/>
            <para>
              <text>Section 54 is amended by adding the following subsection:</text>
              <amend quote="1">
                <subprov skeleton="no">
                  <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">5</label>
                  <para>
                    <text>In this section, <def-term id="DLM1122580">copy</def-term> includes a digital copy, but in that case <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 56C</citation></changeable> applies as well.</text>
                  </para>
