            <para>
              <text>Section 99(1)(a) is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">broadcasts, or includes in a cable programme</amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1">or communicates to the public</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 99(2)(a) is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">broadcasts or includes in a cable programme</amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1">communicates to the public</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">3</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 99(4) is amended by repealing paragraph (a) and substituting the following paragraph:</text>
